Note: Network Working Group S. Deering, Xerox PARC Request for Comments: 1883 R. Hinden, Ipsilon Networks Category: Standards Track  This document specifies version 6 of the Internet Protocol (IPv6), also sometimes referred to as IP Next Generation or IPng. Deering Hinden Standards Track [Page 1] RFC 1883 IPv6 Specification  
